title: Bloomberg Power Players Summit
itunes:title: Bloomberg Power Players Summit
description:
Broadcasting from Miami to discuss sports, technology and more are Premier Lacrosse League Co-Founder Paul Rabil, Jacksonville Jaguars Linebacker Najee Goode, former NBA player Jason Williams, former NFL player Ovie Mughelli, Buffalo Bills Owner Kim Pegula, and John Skipper, Executive Chairman of DAZN and former President at ESPN.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
